```class Solution {
    public int bitwiseComplement(int n) {
        int temp = n, result = 0;
        while (temp > 0) {
            result = (result << 1) | (temp % 2 == 0 ? 1 : 0);
            temp >>= 1;
        }
        return result;
    }
}```
